      <title>摩根大通任命瓦德瓦尼为印度投资银行领导人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/jpmorgan-names-india-investment-bank-leaders-as-wadhwani-leaves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp; Co.) 已提拔两名资深交易员为印度投资银行业务联席主管，以期在纳文·瓦德瓦尼 (Navin Wadhwani) 最近离职后巩固其在市场的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/jpmorgan-names-india-investment-bank-leaders-as-wadhwani-leaves</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 07:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
